#. <section class="sutta" id="sn24.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn24.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 24"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 24"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn24.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Sotāpattivagga"
msgstr "1. Stream-Entry"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn24.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Soattāsutta"
msgstr "3. This Is My Self"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.205"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn24.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn24.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi "
"uppajjati:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on "
"what, does the view arise:"

msgctxt "sn24.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘so attā, so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable’?”"

msgctxt "sn24.3:1.4"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe …."
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn24.3:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Rūpe kho, bhikkhave, sati, rūpaṃ upādāya, rūpaṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi "
"uppajjati:"
msgstr ""
"“When form exists, because of grasping form and insisting on form, the view "
"arises:"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘so attā, so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable.’"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.3"
msgid "Vedanāya sati … pe …"
msgstr "When feeling …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.4"
msgid "saññāya sati …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.5"
msgid "saṅkhāresu sati …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.6"
msgid ""
"viññāṇe sati, viññāṇaṃ upādāya, viññāṇaṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati:"
msgstr ""
"consciousness exists, because of grasping consciousness and insisting on "
"consciousness, the view arises:"

msgctxt "sn24.3:2.7"
msgid ""
"‘so attā, so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn24.3:3.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.2"
msgid "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "Is form permanent or impermanent?”"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.3"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … pe …"
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.4"
msgid "api nu taṃ anupādāya evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.5"
msgid "‘so attā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.6"
msgid "avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.7"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.8"
msgid "“Vedanā …"
msgstr "“Is feeling …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.9"
msgid "saññā …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.10"
msgid "saṅkhārā …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.11"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "consciousness permanent or impermanent?”"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.12"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.13"
msgid "api nu taṃ anupādāya evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.14"
msgid "‘so attā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.15"
msgid "avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.16"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.17"
msgid ""
"“Yampidaṃ diṭṭhaṃ sutaṃ mutaṃ viññātaṃ pattaṃ pariyesitaṃ anuvicaritaṃ "
"manasā tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“That which is seen, heard, thought, cognized, searched, and explored by the "
"mind: is that permanent or impermanent?”"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.18"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.19"
msgid "api nu taṃ anupādāya evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""
"“But by not grasping what’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable, would "
"such a view arise?”"

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.20"
msgid ""
"‘so attā, so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.3:3.21"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn24.3:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa imesu ca ṭhānesu kaṅkhā pahīnā hoti, "
"dukkhepissa kaṅkhā pahīnā hoti … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāyapissa "
"kaṅkhā pahīnā hoti—"
msgstr ""
"“When a noble disciple has given up doubt in these six cases, and has given "
"up doubt in suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the practice that "
"leads to its cessation,"

msgctxt "sn24.3:4.2"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako sotāpanno avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyano”ti."
msgstr ""
"they’re called a noble disciple who is a stream-enterer, not liable to be "
"reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn24.3:4.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
